    "body": "Figured out that I need to specify the `--authrpc.port` parameter to fix the issue:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# mainnet\r\n./build/bin/erigon --datadir=\"<your_mainnet_data_path>\" --chain=mainnet --port=30303 --http.port=8545 --torrent.port=42069 --private.api.addr=127.0.0.1:9090 --authrpc.port=8551 --http --ws --http.api=eth,debug,net,trace,web3,erigon\r\n\r\n\r\n# goerli\r\n./build/bin/erigon --datadir=\"<your_goerli_data_path>\" --chain=goerli --port=30304 --http.port=8546 --torrent.port=42068 --private.api.addr=127.0.0.1:9091 --authrpc.port=8552 --http --ws --http.api=eth,debug,net,trace,web3,erigon\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis should probably be documented in `README`.",
